<li><a href="http://atlas.arbor.net/summary/dos" class="external text" title="http://atlas.arbor.net/summary/dos" rel="nofollow">ATLAS Summary Report</a> - Real-time global report of DDoS attacks.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.linuxsecurity.com/content/view/121960/49/" class="external text" title="http://www.linuxsecurity.com/content/view/121960/49/" rel="nofollow">linuxsecurity.com</a> An article on preventing DDoS attacks.</li>
